classification: John F. Kennedy Assassination Records Act of 1992
summary: This document discusses the release of a classified document related to Lee Harvey Oswald. It mentions a fax received that appears incomplete, including a cover sheet, a cable stating "NO TRACES," and the first page of a Director cable requesting traces on Lee Harvey Oswald. The document also discusses the deletion of crypts and informing the ambassador and liaison service chiefs about the release date.
title: RELEASE OF CLASSIFIED DOCUMENT
